---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Badges & Embeds" description="Add RCAN badges to your GitHub README and documentation.">
  <nav class="doc-nav">
    <a href="/docs/">‚Üê Documentation</a>
  </nav>

  <article class="doc-article">
    <h1>Badges & Embeds</h1>
    <p class="lead">Show your robot's RCAN registration with embeddable badges.</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Badge Styles</h2>
      <p>Three badge styles are available:</p>

      <div class="badge-showcase">
        <div class="badge-item">
          <h3>Flat (Default)</h3>
          <img src="/api/badge/RRN-00000001.svg?style=flat" alt="Flat badge" />
          <code>?style=flat</code>
        </div>
        <div class="badge-item">
          <h3>Flat Square</h3>
          <img src="/api/badge/RRN-00000001.svg?style=flat-square" alt="Flat square badge" />
          <code>?style=flat-square</code>
        </div>
        <div class="badge-item">
          <h3>Plastic</h3>
          <img src="/api/badge/RRN-00000001.svg?style=plastic" alt="Plastic badge" />
          <code>?style=plastic</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Usage</h2>

      <h3>Markdown</h3>
      <pre><code>[![RCAN](https://rcan.dev/api/badge/RRN-XXXXXXXX.svg)](https://rcan.dev/registry/RRN-XXXXXXXX/)</code></pre>

      <h3>HTML</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;a href="https://rcan.dev/registry/RRN-XXXXXXXX/"&gt;
  &lt;img src="https://rcan.dev/api/badge/RRN-XXXXXXXX.svg" alt="RCAN Registry"&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre>

      <h3>reStructuredText</h3>
      <pre><code>.. image:: https://rcan.dev/api/badge/RRN-XXXXXXXX.svg
   :target: https://rcan.dev/registry/RRN-XXXXXXXX/
   :alt: RCAN Registry</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>API Endpoint</h2>
      <pre><code>GET /api/badge/&#123;rrn&#125;.svg</code></pre>

      <h3>Query Parameters</h3>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Parameter</th>
            <th>Values</th>
            <th>Default</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><code>style</code></td>
            <td>flat, flat-square, plastic</td>
            <td>flat</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><code>label</code></td>
            <td>Custom text</td>
            <td>RCAN</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3>Examples</h3>
      <pre><code>/api/badge/RRN-00000001.svg
/api/badge/RRN-00000001.svg?style=plastic
/api/badge/RRN-00000001.svg?label=Robot</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Status Colors</h2>
      <p>Badges are color-coded by robot status:</p>

      <div class="status-colors">
        <div class="status-item">
          <span class="status-dot" style="background: #22c55e;"></span>
          <span><strong>active</strong> - Green</span>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
          <span class="status-dot" style="background: #f59e0b;"></span>
          <span><strong>prototype</strong> - Amber</span>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
          <span class="status-dot" style="background: #8b5cf6;"></span>
          <span><strong>concept</strong> - Purple</span>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
          <span class="status-dot" style="background: #6b7280;"></span>
          <span><strong>retired</strong> - Gray</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Finding Your Badge</h2>
      <p>Every robot's registry page has a "Share & Embed" section with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Pre-generated badge preview</li>
        <li>Copy-to-clipboard Markdown code</li>
        <li>Copy-to-clipboard HTML code</li>
        <li>Links to all badge styles</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Just visit your robot's page at <code>/registry/RRN-XXXXXXXX/</code> and scroll to the bottom.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .doc-nav {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .doc-nav a {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .badge-showcase {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .badge-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .badge-item h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .badge-item img {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }

  .badge-item code {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .status-colors {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .status-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .status-dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .badge-showcase {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .status-colors {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
